{
  "stem": "7093.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I couldn't help myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's the only time when I did something where I behaved in a not civilized way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I am telling this story, because very many people did behave in uncivilized ways through-- through our camp time and everything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I do speak about that, too, if I speak-- speak to any group.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But I always tell them also that I also misbehaved at one point.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And it's the following.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were in the ghetto for seven weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My-- a friend of mine, who trained with me in the same training college, and myself, we collected all the children between two and six.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we were very lucky, because the weather was nice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the synagogue courtyard was within the-- within this ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And so we took all the children, so that they shouldn't be in these terribly cramped conditions.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we tried and played with them and did occupied them, so that during the day they shouldn't be so cooped up in rooms where there were often 12 to 14 persons.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "As I say, we were lucky we were only six in a room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We had very little to eat, but we managed somehow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I still did some so-called bread bags, which was a side bag with a very long [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It was really a shoulder bag, what today is called a shoulder bag.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But we called it bread bag.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I sewed in quite a lot of jewels of people-- big chains, golden chains, and various things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I sewed in for myself also something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But at the last minute, I took it out and put it on the-- under the roof [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in a corner.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It might still be there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
